	<dl>
	<dt>I *AM* voting. If only so I can legitimately...</dt>
	<dd><p>I *AM* voting. If only so I can legitimately complain about the state of the country for the next 4-5 years. Anyone who doesn't vote loses that right. </p>
	<small>
	written 15th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/877">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=877">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

