	<p><em><strong>Mj</strong> replies:</em> </p> <p>SW - you say you are hoping that enough people don't vote to invalidate any resultant mandate to rule.</p> <p>What would this achieve? The country would be in constitutional crisis, with no government to keep shop.</p>
	<small>
	written 18th Apr 2005 <!-- | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=877&amp;commentid=1189">abusive?</a>
